thread.title: Ann, Sydney
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Ann, Sydney

author: Ann, Sydney
title: Ann, Sydney
text: This was my first purchase from Ink Station. I received it the morning following placing my order. I installed the ink cartridges in my inkjet and laser printers immediately and they work beautifully. The quality is excellent, the price is more than satisfactory. Also, emails kept me informed of the status of my order. I will be a returning customer for sure
